<FTL>

<!-- 
=======================
RK BAM
=======================
 -->

<!-- Basically an extra vampiric weapon with various events and RadiKal-style spice. -->
<augBlueprint name="DJMOD_COMBAT_SHIPVORE_RAM">
    <title>Shipvore Ram</title>
    <desc>The signature combat augment of the RadiKal Bam lets you repeatedly ram the enemy for guaranteed quickly lethal damage, free repairs and sometimes other things. WARNING: your ship and/or crew may suffer. [Uses {, full power uses more and destroys the augment. Emergency Generator and Fuel Conserver can apply.]
	Can be reinforced at empty beacons to survive the next Full Power use.
	</desc>
    <cost>70</cost>
	<!--<bp>4</bp>-->
    <rarity>3</rarity>
    <stackable>false</stackable>
</augBlueprint>
<augBlueprint name="LOCKED_DJMOD_COMBAT_SHIPVORE_RAM">
    <title>Shipvore Ram</title>
    <desc>The signature combat augment of the RadiKal Bam lets you repeatedly ram the enemy for guaranteed quickly lethal damage, free repairs and sometimes other things. WARNING: your ship and/or crew may suffer. [Uses {, full power uses more. Emergency Generator and Fuel Conserver can apply.]
	
	The ship was built around this locked version that survives Full Power use. Also gives 9% faster shield recharge and chance to ignore hull damage.
	</desc>
    <cost>200</cost>
    <rarity>0</rarity>
    <stackable>false</stackable>
</augBlueprint>


<augBlueprint name="DJMOD_CREW_ARE_BOMBS_OFF">
    <title>Charged Belts (Off)</title>
    <desc>This augment is Off but can be toggled On anytime. When On: 
	[This double-edged augment from the RadiKal Bam equips your crew with belts that reduce their HP by 10% (beware of Ghosts) and explode when they die, causing a fire and dealing damage to the room and ship they're in, with extra damage in systemless rooms.
	Stacks upon already existing death effects.
	
	Cannot be toggled Off but can scrap itself into ~ or } at empty beacons.

	COMBO: Makes any crew a fire source for Plasma Teleporter.]</desc>
    <cost>50</cost>		
    <rarity>5</rarity>
    <stackable>false</stackable>
</augBlueprint>
<!-- Add combo to only work on enemy ship. Maybe should have charges -->
<augBlueprint name="DJMOD_CREW_ARE_BOMBS_ON">
    <title>Charged Belts</title>
    <desc>This double-edged augment from the RadiKal Bam equips your crew with belts that reduce their HP by 10% (beware of Ghosts) and explode when they die, causing a fire and dealing damage to the room and ship they're in, with extra damage in systemless rooms.
	Stacks upon already existing death effects.
	
	Cannot be toggled Off but can scrap itself into ~ or } at empty beacons.

	COMBO: Makes any crew a fire source for Plasma Teleporter.</desc>
    <cost>50</cost>		
    <rarity>0</rarity>
    <stackable>false</stackable>
</augBlueprint>

<!-- Can trigger immediately if below HP threshold when choosing to activate it in combat check. -->
<augBlueprint name="DJMOD_AUG_AUTO_SYS_REPAIR">
    <title>A.E.R.A. Second Wind</title>
    <desc>'Automated Emergency Repair Augment', by RadiKal Bam engineers. When active, if your ship is almost destroyed (5 hull or less), a nanomachine burst will be released in your systems, fully repairing them as well as 8 hull points, and destroying the augment. No effect if your hull instantly reaches 0. [Activation uses 1 power]</desc>
    <cost>70</cost>
    <rarity>3</rarity>
    <stackable>false</stackable>
</augBlueprint>
</FTL>

