<FTL>
<!-- Each level increases the fire res and adds a full new stat. 
The first one allows widespread own ship fire control and survival, with heal. -->
<augBlueprint name="DJMOD_COMBAT_SCORCH_SELF">
    <title>Scorched Earth (T1)</title>
    <desc>On both ships, this RadiKal Scorch augment makes your crew take 40% less fire damage and get x3 extinguishing. While extinguishing, they also heal 2 HP/second +2 per powered level in O2.
	Activate from the Toggles menu to set specific systems on your ship (or the whole ship) on fire to fight boarders.
	
	COMBO: Plasma Teleporter moves the augment's fire to the enemy ship.
	
	Can be upgraded twice at empty beacons.</desc>
    <cost>75</cost>
    <rarity>3</rarity>
    <stackable>false</stackable>
</augBlueprint>

<!-- Scorched earth upgrade that makes it more offensive and general purpose, with speed & damage -->
<augBlueprint name="DJMOD_COMBAT_SCORCH_SELF_2">
    <title>Blazing Earth (T2)</title>
    <desc>[Tier 2 Scorched Earth] On both ships, this RadiKal Scorch augment makes your crew take 55% less fire damage and get x3 extinguishing. While extinguishing, they also heal 2 HP/second +2 per powered level in O2.
	In fire, they move and sabotage at x2 speed and deal x2 damage.
	Activate from the Toggles menu to set specific systems on your ship (or the whole ship) on fire to fight boarders.
	
	COMBO: Plasma Teleporter moves the augment's fire to the enemy ship.
	
	Can be upgraded once at empty beacons.</desc>
    <cost>120</cost>			
    <rarity>5</rarity>
    <stackable>false</stackable>
</augBlueprint>

<!-- finally adds offensive tools on the enemy ship to actually win, and potential infinity loop. -->
<augBlueprint name="DJMOD_COMBAT_SCORCH_SELF_3">
    <!-- <title>Molten Earth</title> -->
	<title>Erupting Earth (T3)</title>
    <desc>[Tier 3 Scorched Earth] On both ships, this RadiKal Scorch augment makes your crew take 70% less fire damage and get x3 extinguishing. While extinguishing, they also heal 2 HP/second +2 per powered level in O2.
	In fire, they move and sabotage at x2 speed, deal x2 damage, and produce O2 like 2 Orchids.
	Also, enemy crew and drones in fire lose 7 hp per second.
	Activate from the Toggles menu to set specific systems on your ship (or the whole ship) on fire to fight boarders.
	
	COMBO: Plasma Teleporter moves the augment's fire to the enemy ship.</desc>
    <cost>175</cost>
    <rarity>0</rarity>
    <stackable>false</stackable>
</augBlueprint>

<!-- finally adds enemy ship offense to actually win, and potential infinity loop.-->
